\fs20 \cf3 \super \ul \ulc3 \strokec3 [2]}}{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nagarjuna#cite_note-4"}}{\fldrslt 
\fs20 \cf3 \super \ul \ulc3 \strokec3 [4]}} His {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/M%C5%ABlamadhyamakak%C4%81rik%C4%81"}}{\fldrslt 
\f4\i \cf3 \ul \ulc3 \strokec3 M\uc0\u363 lamadhyamakak\u257 rik\u257 }} (Root Verses on Madhyamaka, MMK) is the most important text on the madhyamaka philosophy of {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C5%9A%C5%ABnyat%C4%81"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 \strokec3 emptiness}}.\
